											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[KAYLEIGH] The player slowly steps toward Gale, they both close in for a final kiss and pull each other closer, but then the player pulls away suddenly as though given an electric shock, the power too strong. They reach for their lips in surprise before lowering their hand and looking back at Gale." />
